                    `NOTE:` The pitch and yaw arguments can also accept a `X,Y,Z` coordinate. <br/>
                    `TIP:` Copy the yaw and pitch from the F3 screen in minecraft (the `Facing: Direction (Axis) (Yaw/Pitch)` line).

